OL,4,CNew children's commissioner pledges to
OL,5,C'rebuild' childhood
OL,6, The new children's commissioner for
OL,7, England wants to "rebuild childhood"
OL,8, after the disruption of the pandemic.
OL,10,FDame Rachel de Souza says the scale of
OL,11,Fthe challenge is like reconstructing
OL,12,Fthe social security system in the wake
OL,13,Fof World War Two.
OL,15,FShe also wants short-term measures -
OL,16,Fsuch as free school meals - being
OL,17,Fextended into the summer holidays, and
OL,18,Fnot "dropping" Universal Credit levels.
OL,20,FDame Rachel says she will be "fearless"
OL,21,Fin representing children's interests.
